title: Need members for Nautilus Mains club
body:
{{champion:111}} "Titan's Wrath" club! {{champion:111}} 

This club is meant for Nautilus fans, and is not a serious group, mainly a place where we can share information and play normals together. 
Anyone that plays Nautilus is allowed to join but Level 5 Mastery Nautilus players have priority in being accepted in.

If you want to join just write in the comments below and/or send me a friend request.
